---
import Container from "./Container.astro"
---

<div id="features">
    <Container>
        <div class="md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"
                 class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                      d="M9 4.5a.75.75 0 01.721.544l.813 2.846a3.75 3.75 0 002.576 2.576l2.846.813a.75.75 0 010 1.442l-2.846.813a3.75 3.75 0 00-2.576 2.576l-.813 2.846a.75.75 0 01-1.442 0l-.813-2.846a3.75 3.75 0 00-2.576-2.576l-2.846-.813a.75.75 0 010-1.442l2.846-.813A3.75 3.75 0 007.466 7.89l.813-2.846A.75.75 0 019 4.5zM18 1.5a.75.75 0 01.728.568l.258 1.036c.236.94.97 1.674 1.91 1.91l1.036.258a.75.75 0 010 1.456l-1.036.258c-.94.236-1.674.97-1.91 1.91l-.258 1.036a.75.75 0 01-1.456 0l-.258-1.036a2.625 2.625 0 00-1.91-1.91l-1.036-.258a.75.75 0 010-1.456l1.036-.258a2.625 2.625 0 001.91-1.91l.258-1.036A.75.75 0 0118 1.5zM16.5 15a.75.75 0 01.712.513l.394 1.183c.15.447.5.799.948.948l1.183.395a.75.75 0 010 1.422l-1.183.395c-.447.15-.799.5-.948.948l-.395 1.183a.75.75 0 01-1.422 0l-.395-1.183a1.5 1.5 0 00-.948-.948l-1.183-.395a.75.75 0 010-1.422l1.183-.395c.447-.15.799-.5.948-.948l.395-1.183A.75.75 0 0116.5 15z"
                      clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>

            <h2 class="my-8 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">
                Tutta la nostra esperienza e serietà riassunta in pochi punti
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Affidati a noi per dare nuova vita alle tue serrature:
                installazione, sostituzione e riparazione eseguite con rapidità, professionalità ed economicità, sempre
                con il cliente al centro. Scopri qui tutti i dettagli dei nostri servizi pensati per la tua
                sicurezza</p>
        </div>
        <div
                class="mt-16 grid divide-x divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-700 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 text-gray-600 dark:border-gray-700 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:divide-y-0 xl:grid-cols-2"
        >
            <div class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
                <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
                    <img
                            src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/14846/14846423.png"
                            class="w-12"
                            width="512"
                            height="512"
                            alt="burger illustration"
                    />

                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <h5
                                class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
                        >Serrature di sicurezza
                        </h5>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                            Le nostre serrature sono il nostro fiore all’occhiello: leader nella riparazione,
                            sostituzione e installazione per privati, commerci e imprese.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
                <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
                    <img
                            src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/8037/8037114.png"
                            class="w-12"
                            width="512"
                            height="512"
                            alt="burger illustration"
                    />

                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <h5
                                class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
                        >
                            Porte blindate
                        </h5>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                            Proteggi casa, lavoro e i tuoi cari con una porta blindata di qualità: affidati ai migliori.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
                class="mt-16 grid divide-x divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-700 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 text-gray-600 dark:border-gray-700 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 lg:divide-y-0 xl:grid-cols-4"
        >
            <div class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
                <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
                    <img
                            src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/5285/5285806.png"
                            class="w-12"
                            width="512"
                            height="512"
                            alt="burger illustration"
                    />

                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <h5
                                class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
                        >Serrande
                        </h5>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                            Una serranda guasta può costarti tempo e denaro. Interveniamo subito per risolvere il
                            problema rapidamente.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
                <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
                    <img
                            src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/5532/5532931.png"
                            class="w-12"
                            width="512"
                            height="512"
                            alt="burger illustration"
                    />

                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <h5
                                class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
                        >
                            Interventi rapidi
                        </h5>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                            Cerchi un fabbro affidabile? Scegli noi: pronto intervento a Milano, provincia, Monza e
                            Brianza.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
                <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
                    <img
                            src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2778/2778814.png"
                            class="w-12"
                            width="512"
                            height="512"
                            alt="burger illustration"
                    />

                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <h5
                                class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
                        >
                            Manutenzione
                        </h5>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                            Da oltre 25 anni offriamo assistenza rapida e professionale con tecnici esperti e materiali d’eccellenza.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div
                    class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10"
            >
                <div
                        class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8 transition duration-300 group-hover:bg-white dark:group-hover:bg-gray-800"
                >
                    <img
                            src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/8749/8749126.png"
                            class="w-12"
                            width="512"
                            height="512"
                            alt="burger illustration"
                    />

                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <h5
                                class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary"
                        >Inferiate e cancelli
                        </h5>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                            Scegliere la porta blindata giusta è fondamentale per la sicurezza. Affidati a esperti per
                            qualità, resistenza e protezione.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </Container>
</div>